<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286990>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Fergusobia sporangae n. sp. (all in lateral view): A, Entire parthenogenetic female; B, Head of parthenogenetic female; C, Habitus; D, Tails of parthenogenetic females; E, Entire infective female; F, Head of infective female; G, Habitus; H, Tails of infective females; I, Entire male; J, Head of male; K, Habitus; L, Tails of males. Scale bars: A, E, I = 50 µm. B, F, J = 5 µm. Tails not drawn to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/286990/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286992>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Spicules from Fergusobia spp. collected from small shoot bud galls: A, MSp 40 from E. marginata; B, F. rileyi; C, MSp 61 from E. delegatensis; D, MSp 55 from E. amygdalina; E, MSp 78 from E. blakelyi; F, MSp 59 from E. obliqua; G, MSp 41 from E. pauciflora; H, Fergusobia sp. from ABG from Eucalyptus sp. at Brisbane, QLD; I, MSp 30 from E. tereticornis; J, F. gomphocephalae n. sp.; K, F. leucoxylonae n. sp.; L, F. sporangae n. sp.; M, MSp 21 from E. microcarpae; N, Fergusobia sp. from E. odorata; O, MSp 28 from E.? siderophloia; P, MSp 39 from E. viminalis UABG form 2; Q, MSp 79 from E. fasciculosae; R, MSp 47 from E. cladocalyx; S, MSp 77 from E. confluens; T, Fergusobia sp. from LPG from Eucalyptus sp. at Indooroopilly, Brisbane, QLD; U, F. schmidti n. sp. Not drawn to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/286992/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

